sentences: Thompson-Hannant independently released her first EP, Dear Fear, in 2011 through Bandcamp.
For the two years following this release, she garnered press attention through playing festivals such as SXSW and Pop Montreal.
In February 2013 she released her second EP, Hello, through Merok Records.
In June 2014 she announced a new album, titled Being, for release on August 5 of that year and released the single "Enjoy".
